lobbying_activities:
[{'general_issue_code': 'TAX', 'general_issue_code_display': 'Taxation/Internal Revenue Code', 'description': "Building Efficiency Act - AHRI worked with Congressman Langevin's office on draft proposal for changing the depreciation schedule for energy efficiency upgrades to commercial and rental property buildings.
Tax Proposal - AHRI submitted tax proposal language to the House Ways and Means Committee on efficiency incentives for commercial and residential properties.Home Owner Managing Energy Savings (HOMES) Act - AHRI worked with Congressman Welch and his staff on a draft proposal creating incentives for energy efficiency upgrades.", 'foreign_entity_issues': '', 'lobbyists': [{'lobbyist': {'id': 50189, 'prefix': None, 'prefix_display': None, 'first_name': 'GUIDO', 'nickname': None, 'middle_name': None, 'last_name': 'ZUCCONI', 'suffix': None, 'suffix_display': None}, 'covered_position': None, 'new': False}, {'lobbyist': {'id': 56293, 'prefix': None, 'prefix_display': None, 'first_name': 'CADE', 'nickname': None, 'middle_name': None, 'last_name': 'CLARK', 'suffix': None, 'suffix_display': None}, 'covered_position': None, 'new': False}], 'government_entities': [{'id': 33, 'name': 'Energy, Dept of'}, {'id': 2, 'name': 'HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES'}, {'id': 1, 'name': 'SENATE'}]}, {'general_issue_code': 'ENG', 'general_issue_code_display': 'Energy/Nuclear', 'description': 'S. 721 Energy Savings and Industrial Competiveness Act - AHRI worked with the offices of Senators Shaheen and Portman on portions of draft legislative language, specifically on building codes and a motor rebate program proposal.
Regional Furnace Efficiency Standards - AHRI advocated Congress and the DOE to delay implementation of new furnace efficiency standards in light of ongoing litigation involving those standards.AHRI Member Advocacy Day - AHRI staff accompanied AHRI members on visits to a number of House and Senate offices to discuss industry policy priorities and goals for the 113th Congress.
